~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
This is README file for Configurator (C++ library for configuration file parsing).

Last update: November 30, 2010
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

CONFIGURATOR
version 0.9.2

ABSTRACT
--------

Configurator provides parsing of configuration file, with nesting sections,
allow to define option's default value, option's necessity and option's value semantic check.
For more info see documentation and examples.


EXTERNAL DEPENDENCIES
---------------------

Only "one" - Boost C++ libraries. See documentation.

 
PORTABILITY
-----------

It is portable so far as portable Boost C++ libraries and C++ standard library. :-)


WEBSITE
-------

See http://opensource.dshevchenko.biz/configurator for all info.


MORE INFORMATION
----------------

Sourceforge page: 	http://sourceforge.net/projects/cfo-parser/
Author's site: 		http://opensource.dshevchenko.biz
 
